{"tid":701149,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女友聲稱被強姦　男警涉案重案調查","createTime":"2018-06-14T01:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T02:03:59.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"df5d802c612fd8ef695fd610c6c2435d50773178","tid":701149,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T01:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180613/photo/bkn-20180613210556287-0613_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180613233736\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180613%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180613210556287-0613_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180613233736&h=7c00b421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名女子昨日(12日)報案，聲稱遭一名男子強姦。據悉，涉案男子為一名警員，駐守黃大仙警區，港島總區重案組接手跟進。至今日（13日），重案組探員到黃大仙警署，向涉案男警了解事件經過。 <br />\n<br />\n消息指，涉案男警已婚，早前結識女事主並發展感情，雙方曾發生性關係，惟女事主事後卻聲稱在不願意的情況下，與人發生性行為，遂報警求助。 <br />\n<br />\n警方發言人表示，在6月12日接獲一名33歲女子報案，案件暫列作「求警調查」，由港島總區重案組接手調查，暫未有人被捕。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180613/bkn-20180613210556287-0613_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180613%2Fbkn-20180613210556287-0613_00822_001.html&d=jSaVrvWmoXwvmhgKSppV09Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=07ed9d1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180613/bkn-20180613210556287-0613_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9d6b6852827f25c46c3747ac70eeadc5d732fdc3","tid":701149,"uid":36296,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T02:01:01.000Z","msg":"勞資糾紛"},{"pid":"058411e4826480dbca0c19445a91f2e5f3525609","tid":701149,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T02:03:59.000Z","msg":"搜下你有冇違禁品收埋喺塊西道咋,差人做嘢唔使你教"}]}